OL,3,CBody found in search for British man,
OL,4,C23, missing while swimming in Portugal
OL,6,FA body has been found in the search
OL,7,Ffor a 23-year-old British man who went
OL,8,Fmissing while swimming in the sea in
OL,9,FPortugal last week, local authorities
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FThe man disappeared on Thursday while
OL,13,Fswimming at Peneco Beach in Albufeira,
OL,14,Fon Portugal's southern coast,
OL,15,Faccording to the country's National
OL,16,FMaritime Authority.
OL,18,FA body, believed to be that of the
OL,19,Fmissing man, was recovered on Tuesday
OL,20,Fafternoon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
