OL,3,CBody found in search for British man,
OL,4,C23, missing while swimming in Portugal
OL,6,F"Following an alert at 6.37 pm from a
OL,7,Ffisherman in the vicinity, officers
OL,8,Ffrom the Portimao Local Maritime
OL,9,FPolice Command, the Albufeira
OL,10,FVolunteer Firefighters' Humanitarian
OL,11,FAssociation and the Albufeira
OL,12,FMunicipal Civil Protection Service
OL,13,Fwere mobilised," Portuguese police
OL,14,Fsaid in a statement.
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
