PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781700487
OL,3,CBody found in search for British man,
OL,4,C23, missing while swimming in Portugal
OL,6,F"On arrival at the scene, members of
OL,7,Fthe Maritime Police, in collaboration
OL,8,Fwith the Fire Brigade, transported the
OL,9,Fvictim to Albufeira Marina."
OL,11,FA local Maritime Police official said:
OL,12,F"Death was confirmed at the scene and,
OL,13,Ffollowing contact with the Public
OL,14,FProsecutor's Office, the body was
OL,15,Ftransported by the Fire Brigade to the
OL,16,FNational Institute of Legal Medicine
OL,17,Fand Forensic Sciences of the Western
OL,18,FAlgarve.
OL,20,F"The British Consulate in Portimao was
OL,21,Fcontacted and informed of the incident.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@\O]tD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
