OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781700487
OL,3,CBody found in search for British man,
OL,4,C23, missing while swimming in Portugal
OL,6,F"The Maritime Police's Portimao Local
OL,7,FCommand took charge of the incident."
OL,9,FThe Foreign, Commonwealth and
OL,10,FDevelopment Office has been contacted
OL,11,Ffor comment.
OL,13,FA search had been underway for the
OL,14,Fmissing man since last Friday,
OL,15,Faccording to the National Maritime
OL,16,FAuthority.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@eO]
