OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781700487
OL,3,CBody found in search for British man,
OL,4,C23, missing while swimming in Portugal
OL,6,FThe service previously said the 23-
OL,7,Fyear-old had been accompanied by a 19-
OL,8,Fyear-old British national "who
OL,9,Fapparently managed to get out of the
OL,10,Fwater by his own means to seek help
OL,11,Fafter which the other one disappeared".
